Necesitamos un ejemplito de crear y usar una DBF desde el mod :pray:
Example from Cristobal to build and use DBFs, could someone test it ? thanks

#xcommand ? <cText> => AP_RPuts( <cText> )

#define CRLF hb_OsNewLine()

REQUEST DBFCDX

PROCEDURE Main()

  LOCAL aRdd := rddList()
  LOCAL cRdd := " "

  LOCAL aStruct := { ;
     { "CHARACTER", "C", 25, 0 }, ;
     { "NUMERIC",   "N",  8, 0 }, ;
     { "DOUBLE",    "N",  8, 2 }, ;
     { "DATE",      "D",  8, 0 }, ;
     { "LOGICAL",   "L",  1, 0 } }

  SET EXCLUSIVE OFF

  ? "Registered RDD's:", hb_ntos( Len( aRdd ) ), "=>"
  AEval( aRdd, { | cDriver | cRdd += cDriver } )
  ? cRdd
  rddSetDefault( "DBFCDX" )
  dbCreate( "testdbf", aStruct, "DBFCDX" )
  dbUseArea( , , "testdbf.dbf", "ALIAS_1" )
  ? Bof()
  dbSelectArea( 2 )
  dbUseArea( , "SDF", "testdbf.dbf", "ALIAS_2" )
  dbSelectArea( 3 )
  dbUseArea( , "DELIM", "testdbf.dbf", "ALIAS_3" )
  ? Eof()
  dbSelectArea( 4 )
  dbUseArea( , "DBFNTX", "testdbf.dbf", "ALIAS_4" )
  ? Found()
  dbGoBottom()
  dbGoto( 1 )
  dbSelectArea( 5 )
  dbUseArea( , "DBF", "testdbf.dbf", "ALIAS_5" )
  dbGoTop()
  dbSkip()
  dbCloseArea()
  dbCloseAll()
  hb_dbDrop( "testdbf",, "DBFCDX" )

RETURN
